00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:33,241
They have not gone home, not taken food, nothing.

496
00:41:33,742 --> 00:41:36,283
Just meditating, taking vibrations, correcting.

497
00:41:36,283 --> 00:41:37,950
I am sleeping inside.

498
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:40,199
In the night I want to go to the bathroom,

499
00:41:40,199 --> 00:41:42,325
I just cannot go because they are all meditating.

500
00:41:42,366 --> 00:41:44,533
Nobody is sleeping, nobody is sleeping.

501
00:41:50,950 --> 00:41:53,241
So it is the other way around.

502
00:41:54,199 --> 00:41:56,867
So to you people let us do one day.

