00:43:25,034 --> 00:43:29,199
You think more about it, then you get upset.

518
00:43:29,200 --> 00:43:31,241
You just don't think about it, then you'll enjoy it.

519
00:43:31,241 --> 00:43:32,783
It's like swimming.

