525
00:43:59,159 --> 00:44:03,200
you have to go to bed till 12 o'clock.

526
00:44:03,241 --> 00:44:05,200
Get up at 12 o'clock.

527
00:44:05,241 --> 00:44:09,199
You see the first half of the night, one must sleep always, it's better.

528
00:44:09,408 --> 00:44:13,700
Second half of the night is the better part, alright?

529
00:44:13,909 --> 00:44:17,075
So the first half of the night you all have to sleep, anytime.

530
00:44:17,117 --> 00:44:20,200
You can sleep about 8 o'clock or 9 o'clock if you want to.

531
00:44:22,742 --> 00:44:25,950
But that should not be important, what time you sleep,

532
00:44:25,950 --> 00:44:29,075
you have to get up at 12 o'clock in the morning,

533
00:44:29,742 --> 00:44:31,909
or say after 12.

534
00:44:35,783 --> 00:44:38,867
Shri Krishna was born in the night about 12 o'clock.

535
00:44:38,867 --> 00:44:41,075
Nanaka was born 12 o'clock in the night.

536
00:44:41,075 --> 00:44:45,283
All the Gurus mostly took their birth at 12 o'clock in the night.

537
00:44:46,117 --> 00:44:51,742
To celebrate that, we must have one day when we do not sleep after 12.

538
00:44:52,408 --> 00:44:56,199
But then what about Caxton Hall!

539
00:44:56,658 --> 00:44:59,742
"Mother we can try this on Saturday.

540
00:44:59,825 --> 00:45:01,325
¿What?

541
