682
00:55:08,366 --> 00:55:13,533
every one of them, whether he was a labourer or every one of them,

683
00:55:13,575 --> 00:55:18,075
1000 rupees minimum. Up to 21 000.

684
00:55:18,825 --> 00:55:22,034
In 3 years time they had saved,

685
00:55:22,075 --> 00:55:23,950
because they thought it is our responsibility

686
00:55:23,992 --> 00:55:25,575
to save money for Sahaja Yoga.

687
00:55:25,617 --> 00:55:27,992
Tomorrow if we have to have an ashram how are we going to have ?

688
00:55:33,199 --> 00:55:35,950
But we still indulge into things.

689
00:55:43,742 --> 00:55:48,075
So this is what is the Gurupada.

690
00:55:48,117 --> 00:55:53,992
This Sir has to sit down, make an space for him.

691
00:55:54,034 --> 00:55:57,575
Come on, please. He doesn't need to be stand up. All right.

692
00:56:01,700 --> 00:56:05,366
So today is such a great day of Guru Nanaka's birthday,

693
00:56:06,325 --> 00:56:10,491
and we have to see his own life, how he spent his own life,

694
00:56:10,825 --> 00:56:16,992
how he lived and in what conditions he managed.

695
00:56:19,199 --> 00:56:24,034
So the first thing is to look after, disciplining yourself,

696
00:56:24,617 --> 00:56:28,283
feeling responsible for Sahaja Yoga.

697
00:56:29,117 --> 00:56:33,075
I was amazed people told, me that in the ashram

698
00:56:33,117 --> 00:56:38,199
people keep the lights on, and the oil costs so much,

699
00:56:38,200 --> 00:56:43,159
300 pounds every week. I'm amazed!

700
00:56:44,450 --> 00:56:48,700
Every one of you should be responsi-be for every electricity,

701
00:56:48,700 --> 00:56:52,408
everything that you spend here. This is God's place.

702
00:56:56,159 --> 00:57:00,325
Somebody has given the car, everybody wants to use the car.

703
00:57:00,366 --> 00:57:02,658
You see this saving the pounds

704
00:57:02,700 --> 00:57:05,117
is still going on the heads of Sahaja Yogis.

705
00:57:05,950 --> 00:57:09,117
If they can save by taking somebody's car they would borrow.

706
00:57:09,159 --> 00:57:10,575
Never borrow anybody's car.

707
00:57:10,575 --> 00:57:12,950
It's not for you, you must have your self respect,

708
00:57:12,950 --> 00:57:14,617
why to borrow anybody's car?

709
00:57:14,617 --> 00:57:16,992
It's not to be done.

710
00:57:20,199 --> 00:57:24,034
So the second point of the Self is self respect.

711
00:57:24,617 --> 00:57:27,783
First is the respect of your body,

712
00:57:28,325 --> 00:57:30,867
and the second is self-respect.

713
00:57:34,617 --> 00:57:38,825
We are arrogant, we can be rude,

714
00:57:40,658 --> 00:57:42,491
but we have no self respect.

715
00:57:51,617 --> 00:57:54,783
But it is the training that is lacking,

716
00:57:55,450 --> 00:57:57,783
you see suddenly I find after war

717
00:57:57,783 --> 00:58:03,992
there has been no teaching how to be self respecting.

718
00:58:06,199 --> 00:58:11,408
Like in the war, might be, the atmosphere might have been created I don't know why - that-

719
00:58:11,408 --> 00:58:14,117
"I´m above everything, don't care for others."

720
00:58:17,034 --> 00:58:20,199
May have been; I don't know why this kind of a thing has come,

721
00:58:20,199 --> 00:58:22,325
but it is so. Very prevalent.

722
00:58:22,366 --> 00:58:24,783
But you people have to be other way round:

723
00:58:25,283 --> 00:58:28,700
'Others are first and then yourself.

724
00:58:28,700 --> 00:58:30,325
With your self respect.

725
00:58:30,325 --> 00:58:33,658
Doesn't matter, nobody is going to die, I can tell you this much.

726
00:58:40,408 --> 00:58:45,366
You all must have self respect; and such mediocre people

727
00:58:45,825 --> 00:58:48,491
should not be allowed to stay in Sahaja Yoga,

728
00:58:51,199 --> 00:58:56,325
at least in the ashram, because it brings a bad name to all Sahaja Yoga.

729
00:58:56,325 --> 00:58:58,450
One person can spoil the whole.

730
00:58:58,950 --> 00:59:03,283
Only people who want to be Gurus have to stay in the ashram.

731
00:59:03,325 --> 00:59:06,117
It's not going to be made a convenience for anyone.

732
00:59:08,283 --> 00:59:12,199
But the other way around is that,

733
00:59:12,200 --> 00:59:14,825
"We are going to look after ourselves,

734
00:59:14,867 --> 00:59:17,950
we have to become this, we have to grow,

735
00:59:17,992 --> 00:59:19,658
we have to do it."

736
00:59:25,199 --> 00:59:29,159
Then it's just, the other way round, everything works out,

737
00:59:29,199 --> 00:59:31,034
I don't have to tell you.

738
00:59:31,075 --> 00:59:33,408
You know this is so base and so gross

739
00:59:33,867 --> 00:59:35,783
that after being here for so many years,

740
00:59:36,533 --> 00:59:41,199
you should all have become avadhutas by now, absolutely.

741
00:59:41,199 --> 00:59:43,700
Controlling all elements, everything, should have been possible;

742
